  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>The touch of your shadow-wreathed hand can siphon life &amp;Reference[force]{force} from others to heal your wounds. Make a melee spell attack against a creature within your reach. On a hit, the target takes 3d6 &amp;Reference[necrotic]{necrotic} damage, and you regain hit points equal to half the amount of &amp;Reference[necrotic]{necrotic} damage dealt. Until the spell ends, you can make the attack again on each of your turns as an action.</p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th level or higher, the damage increases by 1d6 for each slot level above 3rd.</p>\n</div>",
